<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10594328>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Dasyhelea bifida Zilahi-Sebess. (A–E) adult male, (F–K) adult female. (A, F) head; (B, G) flagellum; (C) thorax and legs; (D, J) wing; (E) gentalia;(H) palpus; (I) scutellum;(K) abdominal segment 8–9. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10594328/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10594330>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Dasyhelea bifida Zilahi-Sebess. (A–B, D–F) adult male, (C) adult female. (A), genitalia, lateral view; (B), genitalia, ventral, view; (C) abdominal segment 8–9, lateral view; (D) genitalia, dorsal view; (E) paramere; (F) aedeagus. Scale bars: 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10594330/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

